Cell["\<\
Let O = X(3) and suppose that P is a point other than O. Let OP be the circle \
with segment PO as diameter. Let A\[CloseCurlyQuote] be the point of \
intersection, other than O, of OP and the perpendicular bisector of segment \
BC, and define B\[CloseCurlyQuote] and C\[CloseCurlyQuote] cyclically.\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{
  3.978691872231702*^9},ExpressionUUID->"63a3bcae-133c-47e0-b0f9-\
eabe43df33a7"],

